title: Are the Warriors ready for tip-off?
text:
Photo: Carlos Avila Gonzalez, The Chronicle Stephen Curry (right) chats with Warriors interim head coach Luke Walton Tuesday in Oakland. Stephen Curry (right) chats with Warriors interim head coach Luke...
LOS ANGELES — It seemed a bit strange. Tom Thibodeau, one of the NBA’s most respected coaches but currently out of work, has been touring selected training camps and after spending a couple of days with the Warriors over the weekend, he returned to the team’s practice Wednesday.
